<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>로그인</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>로그인</h1>
      <form action="/login" method="post">
        <div>
          <label for="id">아이디</label>
          <input type="email" id="id" name="id" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="password">아이디</label>
          <input type="password" id="password" />
        </div>
        <button type="submit">로그인하기</button>
      </form>

      <div>
        <div>
          <p>아이디가 없으세요?</p>
          <a href="/entry">회원 가입하기</a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p>비밀번호를 잊어버리셨나요?</p>
          <a href="/find">비밀번호 찾기</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
